Disaster Management and the Midvaal Municipality offered help following the
tornado.MEC for Cooperative Governance and Traditional Affairs and
Human Settlements Paul Mashatile visited the area together with Midvaal Mayor
Bongani Baloyi.Mashatile said that information compiled by disaster
management so far,  indicated that  565 shacks were damaged with an estimation of
